## ðŸ”© Hardware Requirements

| Component | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| **Arduino Uno** | Main microcontroller to process commands |
| **AI Thinker VC-02 Voice Module** | Offline voice recognition (stores 50+ commands) |
| **Relay Module (5V)** | To control AC appliances like fan, bulb, TV, etc. |
| **LED / KED Bulb** | Indicator or test appliance |
| **Fan / Other Appliances** | (Optional) Real device control demo |
| **Jumper Wires (Maleâ€“Male / Maleâ€“Female)** | All circuit connections |
| **Breadboard** | Prototyping circuit connections |
| **5V Power Bank / 5V Battery** | For portable and independent power supply |
| **USB Cable (Type B)** | To connect Arduino to laptop (power + upload code) |
| **Microphone (Built-in in VC-02)** | For voice command input |
| **3.3V/5V Logic Compatibility** | VC-02 and Arduino compatible voltage levels |

